{
 "name": "RPlog_Revenge_in_the_Subway",
 "title": "Revenge in the Subway",
 "summary": "In an enclosed underground train station, warm against the blizzard outside, the Izin Ezkhil makes his way along the platform with a precious ticket, just as two ten-man teams of well-equipped troopers charge in, weapons ready. The officer Danik Kreldin, in CDC insignia, strides in behind them and orders his squad leaders to spread out, shut down the tram service, and hunt their quarry down level by level. As civilians scream and scatter in panic, the assault teams prepare to breach with flashbangs and tear gas, and Ezkhil backpedals against the wall to evade the closing trap. The hunt for vengeance plays out through the stark, domed chambers of the subway.",
